##CartService:

The cart should not be sending to recommending service and ad service.

###Related functions: _CartService_GetCart_Handler

CartItem AddItemRequest GetCartRequest Cart 

##ProductCatalog Service:
The product response should not be sent to recommendation and ad service.
### Related functions Getproduct:SearchProducts SearchProductsResponse

## Shipping service:

The shipping address should only be available to checkout service, email service, shipping address

message GetQuoteRequest GetQuoteResponse ShipOrderRequest ShipOrderResponse restricted to shipping service


## CheckoutSevice

order placed be restricted to checkoutservice only 
PlaceOrderRequest 

## PaymentSevice

ChargeRequest contains credit card info. only to paymentservice

## EmailService
send out order confirmation. restrict to only emailservice 